reviewText: Great shape and the movie played well however the pal play wasn't the best.
I love dogs and this set is the best of all. I love the relationship between Jerry Lee and Dooley. He's so funny he makes me literally laugh out loud. This dvd is a true winner.

Didn't even KNOW there was a different dvd format... Yet when my dvd player can't read it... That is what support tells me.  SURPRISE!!! No refund... Just screwed.  This is NOT the dvd format used throughout the USA.
